article.description: — Max Mackinnon's 22 points helped Elon defeat William & Mary 66-55 on Saturday.
article.headline: Mackinnon's 22 help Elon down William & Mary 66-55
article.linkText: Mackinnon's 22 help Elon down William & Mary 66-55
article.story:
ELON, N.C. -- — Max Mackinnon's 22 points helped Elon defeat William & Mary 66-55 on Saturday.

Mackinnon added nine rebounds for the Phoenix (6-20, 4-9 Colonial Athletic Association). Sean Halloran scored 18 points and Sam Sherry finished with 14 points.

The Tribe (9-17, 4-9) were led in scoring by Tyler Rice, who finished with 13 points. William & Mary also got 12 points from Miguel Ayesa and 11 points from Ben Wight.

------
